title: 02/16/2021 – Hour 1 – What Is Wentz Worth
itunes:title: 02/16/2021 – Hour 1 – What Is Wentz Worth
description:
Rob Parker and TJ Houshmandzadeh are in for Dan Patrick and the Danettes, and the guys kick off the show by trying to make sense of the Carson Wentz trade saga as the Bears and the Colts seem to be vying for the quarterback! Former NFL DE Chris Canty joins the show to get his input on the Wentz trade possibilities, and Nets PG Kyrie Irving may finally be showing some signs of maturity!
